					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8670532#post-4061481</guid>
				<title>It&#039;s good.</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8670532/scp-4325#post-4061481</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 18 Nov 2018 03:26:44 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>WORKAHOLIC6</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4736089</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I like this SCP. It's written well, it's an interesting idea, and I like the interview logs. The only thing I would change is that instead of writing &quot;Interviewer&quot;, you need to write the name of the interviewer. For example.</p> <blockquote> <p><strong>Dr/Researcher/Agent Name:</strong> Text</p> </blockquote> <p>Instead of</p> <blockquote> <p><strong>Interviewer:</strong> Text</p> </blockquote> <p>Other than that, I can't find anything else I would change.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
